[8.26, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[8.41, "o", "\u001b[1m  ## \u001b[36mgpt-5.4\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[8.56, "o", "  The change\u2019s stated contr"]
[8.887, "o", "act is wrong. The docstring"]
[9.214, "o", " says \u201cRetries failed batch"]
[9.541, "o", "es up\r\n  to `maxRetries` ti"]
[9.868, "o", "mes,\u201d but the implementatio"]
[10.195, "o", "n does not provide that beh"]
[10.522, "o", "avior.\r\n  \r\n  1. `docs/demo"]
[10.848, "o", "-diff/batch-processor.ts:13"]
[11.175, "o", "`\r\n     - problem: The loop"]
[11.502, "o", " uses `i <= total`, which r"]
[11.829, "o", "uns one iteration past the "]
[12.156, "o", "last real\r\n  batch and invo"]
[12.483, "o", "kes `handler` with `[]`. Th"]
[12.81, "o", "is also happens for `items."]
[13.137, "o", "length === 0`,\r\n  where the"]
[13.464, "o", " function still calls `hand"]
[13.791, "o", "ler` once.\r\n     - conseque"]
[14.118, "o", "nce: Callers that assume ev"]
[14.445, "o", "ery batch is non-empty or t"]
[14.772, "o", "hat `batchIndex` is\r\n  in r"]
[15.098, "o", "ange will misbehave, and an"]
[15.425, "o", " empty input still triggers"]
[15.752, "o", " side effects.\r\n     - conf"]
[16.079, "o", "idence: high\r\n  \r\n  2. `doc"]
[16.406, "o", "s/demo-diff/batch-processor"]
[16.733, "o", ".ts:18-29`\r\n    \u2026\r\n"]
[17.36, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[17.51, "o", "\u001b[1m  ## \u001b[36mgemini-3-flash\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[17.66, "o", "  The implementation of `p"]
[17.987, "o", "rocessBatches` contains se"]
[18.314, "o", "veral critical logic error"]
[18.641, "o", "s and\r\n  lacks necessary g"]
[18.968, "o", "uards, leading to redundan"]
[19.295, "o", "t execution, potential inf"]
[19.622, "o", "inite loops, and\r\n  crypti"]
[19.948, "o", "c failures.\r\n  \r\n  ### Pre"]
[20.275, "o", "mise Disagreement\r\n  The f"]
[20.602, "o", "unction fails to define th"]
[20.929, "o", "e behavior for `items = []"]
[21.256, "o", "` or invalid parameters\r\n "]
[21.583, "o", " (`batchSize <= 0`). It as"]
[21.91, "o", "sumes the caller always pr"]
[22.237, "o", "ovides positive integers a"]
[22.564, "o", "nd non-\r\n  empty arrays, w"]
[22.891, "o", "hich is a dangerous assump"]
[23.218, "o", "tion for a utility functio"]
[23.545, "o", "n. Furthermore, the\r\n  ret"]
[23.872, "o", "ry logic is inefficient by"]
[24.198, "o", " sleeping after the final "]
[24.525, "o", "failure.\r\n  \r\n  ---\r\n  \r\n "]
[24.852, "o", " ### Findings\r\n  \r\n  - **l"]
[25.179, "o", "ocation**: `processBatches"]
[25.506, "o", ":14` (`for (let i = 0; i <"]
[25.833, "o", "= total; i++)`)\r\n    \u2026\r\n"]
[26.46, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[26.61, "o", "\u001b[1m  ## \u001b[36mgpt-5.4-mini\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[26.76, "o", "  This does not satisfy the"]
[27.087, "o", " stated behavior. It proces"]
[27.414, "o", "ses an extra empty batch, a"]
[27.741, "o", "nd the\r\n  retry contract is"]
[28.068, "o", " off by one.\r\n  \r\n  - locat"]
[28.395, "o", "ion: `docs/demo-diff/batch-"]
[28.722, "o", "processor.ts:13-14`\r\n    pr"]
[29.048, "o", "oblem: `for (let i = 0; i <"]
[29.375, "o", "= total; i++)` iterates one"]
[29.702, "o", " past the last real batch.\r"]
[30.029, "o", "\n  Combined with `Math.ceil"]
[30.356, "o", "`, this guarantees a traili"]
[30.683, "o", "ng empty batch for exact mu"]
[31.01, "o", "ltiples\r\n  and also for non"]
[31.337, "o", "-multiples.\r\n    consequenc"]
[31.664, "o", "e: `handler` is invoked wit"]
[31.991, "o", "h empty arrays and a batch "]
[32.318, "o", "index that does not\r\n  corr"]
[32.645, "o", "espond to real data, which "]
[32.972, "o", "can trigger spurious side e"]
[33.298, "o", "ffects or failures after al"]
[33.625, "o", "l\r\n  real work is done.\r\n  "]
[33.952, "o", "  confidence: high\r\n  \r\n  -"]
[34.279, "o", " location: `docs/demo-diff/"]
[34.606, "o", "batch-processor.ts:18-26`\r\n"]
[34.933, "o", "    \u2026\r\n"]
[35.56, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[35.76, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[32m  \u2713 Convergence\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[2m \u2014 all models flagged: \u001b[0m\u001b[36mretry\u001b[0m\u001b[2m, \u001b[0m\u001b[36mlastError\u001b[0m\u001b[2m, \u001b[0m\u001b[36mattempt\u001b[0m\r\n"]
